description:
Your job

- Develop Passive Electronic Component with more on EMC Components, Power Magnetics, Capacitors Market in Hong Kong and Southern China;
- Identify customer needs, market trends and analyze competitors;
- Feedback with market competition status, making sales/account analysis to form up strategy;
- Action items to improve our penetration;
- Meeting target sales plan annually and frequent managing of reports and forecast;
- Develop market strategy and identify new business opportunities to achieve continuous growth;
- Identify areas of improvement and problem solving;
- Build company reputation and brand in the region;
- Reporting to District manager and working in all aspects of marketing events;
- Frequent travel to southern china;  

Your professional background

- Degree or Diploma in Electronics/Electrical or equivalent;
- Over 2 years working experience in Sales of Electronic Components;
- Experience in EMC Components / Power Magnetics / Capacitors / passive components is a must, experience with Hardware Design-In is preferred;
- Good Technical knowledge and strong ability in development and design in supports to Customers in the Region; Integrity, Hardworking, Self-motivated and Analytical;
- Excellent verbal and written communication skills;
- Proficiency in English and Mandarin;

 Your opportunity

The job will be based in HK. To support as a qualified internal administration, you will have the opportunity to participate actively in the growth of our company. We will offer you a salary that is based on performance and oriented to success, along with the benefits you would expect from a modern company.

Your application

We look forward to receiving your application materials (preferably by email). Please indicate your earliest possible start date and the current and salary expectation in your application and submit by Apply Now.


All applications will be treated in strict confidence and personal data collected will be used for recruitment purpose only*

Responsibilities:

Liaise with overseas customers in order confirmation and handle their daily enquiries;
Communicate with China factories and internal parties;
Ensure accurate and on-time production orders, order status reports and delivery time schedule, etc;
Coordinate samples development and delivery on time and prepare for customer presentation;
Follow up the whole merchandising process from product development until production;
Prepare product related documents and reports;
Handle ad hoc assignments as required.

Requirements:

High diploma or above in Sales and Marketing or related discipline;
Minimum 2 years experience of merchandising or manufacturing trading in TOYS ;
Familiar with US & EU market will be advantage;
Strong interpersonal and time management skill;
Well-organized, self-motivated, flexible and able to work independently;
Good PC skill (MS Word, Excel, PowerPoint & Chinese WP is essential);
Immediate available is preferred.

Attractive salary package will be offered to the right candidates. 

Interested parties. Please send your full resume including current and expected salary by clicking “Apply Now”.   Personal data will be collected for recruitment purpose only.

Learn us more at www.winfun.com

 Our company are seeking for talents to fill up our Account Management positions to follow up major accounts in Hong Kong and/or Mainland China. For any interested parties, please see below details:

Responsibilities:

Maintain and develop the existing customer relationship; cultivate and develop potential customers;
Managing existing accounts to attain maximum customers satisfaction, follow up customers' needs and also provide post sales support to existing accounts;
Support the District Sales Director for big projects/ deals;
Recent sales projects follow up and arrangement;
Develop and explore business opportunities; 
Solution proposal, conference calls, business negotiation and close deals both individually and as a team; 
Adding as the communication bridge between Suppliers and Customers 

Requirements:

University graduated is preferred but not a must;
Experience in IT and/or telecommunications;
Experience in Aviation industry is an advantage;
Client management skills with experience in dealing with management executives and/or leaders;
Confident personality to work in project team and project handling experience is an advantage;
Well-developed interpersonal skills, with an ability to communicate well at all organizational levels, foreign suppliers and customers (Greater China and oversea);
Documents and sales materials preparation including translation between Chinese and English;
Good command of using both English and Chinese 
Good command in Putonghua and willing for occasional travelling to China is an advantange
Candidates with less experience and fresh graduates will also be considered for the Account Executive post. 

We offer attractive benefits (including health care) and excellent career development opportunities to our team members. Five days work a week. Salary and benefits will be commensurate with qualifications and experience. Interested parties please provide your resume & recent photo together with present and expected salary and date available

To cope with our rapid business expansion, as a dynamic and friendly firm in integrated digital marketing industry, we would like to invite professional candidates with a keen interest to develop a career with us.

Job Description

Develop long-term relationship with our existing clients and further growing it by devising new digital solutions;
Deliver excellent pre-sales & after-sales service to both existing and new clients;
Adopt consultative approach to customers on their digital marketing & advertising strategies with big data research and analysis;
Plan, implement, and execute business development plans in line with the company’s business goals;
Work towards KPIs and OKRs.

The Successful Applicant

University Graduate;
Minimum 2 years business development or marketing experiences in big data/media / advertising /publishing industry;
Solid experience in devising digital solutions;
Strong project management, organizational, analytical and problem-solving mindset and technique;
Excellent communication, interpersonal and negotiation skills;
Self-motivated, creative and fast learner;
Immediate availability is preferred;
Candidate with higher qualification or working experience in relevant industries will be considered as Senior Account Manager / Account Director.

What's On Offer

Attractive Remuneration Package and Benefits
5-day work
Bank Holidays and other special leave (e.g. Birthday Leave, Wedding Leave and Family Leave, etc.)
Medical Insurance
Sales and Product training will be provided
Team Building Activities
Opportunity for Job Promotion
Friendly Work Environment
Interest parties please send your CV with availability, current and expected salary to us.

**Personal data collected will be used for recruitment purpose only**

Responsibilities:
Achieve business targets with an aligned company strategy;
Identify business opportunities and work closely with cross-functional team (Marketing and Customer service) to realize those opportunities on project basis;
Develop and maintain good customer relationships with assigned key account;
Control trade spending and maximize business opportunities as well as our product presence at shop front;
Ensure promotion activities are well executed at retailer level;
Maintain inventory / transaction records with coordination with Sales & Account team.
Requirements:
Higher Diploma or Above;
At least 3 years sales experience, with experience in FMCG/Retail industry is definitely an advantage;
Good interpersonal and communication skills, self-motivated, independent, responsible and well-organized;
Willing to learn and able to work under pressure;
Fluent in spoken and written English, Mandarin and Cantonese in essential;
Experience in E-Commerce will be an advantage;
Candidate with more experiences will be considered as Senior Key Account Executive.
We offer 5-day-work week with competitive remuneration and benefit packages to the right candidate. Interested parties please send your application letter, resume, expected salary (quoting Employer Ref:) and availability to HR Department at 8/F, Chuan Kei Factory Building, Nos. 15-23, Kin Hong Street, Kwai Chung, NT, HK. or e-mail or browse our website: www.hungfooktong.com.
Personal Information Collection Statement-Applicants’ personal information will be used for the recruitment and employment matters only; information will be kept in strict confidence; information of unsuccessful applicants will be shredded after recruitment process; subject to provisions under the Personal Data (Privacy) Ordinance, applicants have right to access and make corrections of their personal data.

Responsibilities:


Explore new business opportunities through cold call, participation in fairs and website checking and maintain a solid client rapport;
Be well-versed in preparing PowerPoint presentation;
Participate in client meeting and client visit;
Provide contribution to sustain current clients;
Ad hoc project assigned.

Requirements:


Higher Diploma or above in BBA, Science and Pharmaceutical or related disciplines;
Good interpersonal and communication skills to establish good relationship with clients;
Well-organized, proactive, aggressive;
Initiative, self-motivated and strong business sense;
Excellent spoken and written English & Mandarin;
Fresh graduate will also be considered;

We offer attractive remuneration package and excellent career opportunities to the right candidates. Interested parties please send your full resume with availability, current and expected salary to our HR Department.

Welcome to visit our company website http://www.cmatesting.org/ for more information.

We are an Equal Opportunities Employer and welcome applications from all qualified candidates. All Personal data collected will be kept in strict confidence and used for recruitment purpose only.

